description:
You are a property manager auditing compliance for Section 8 housing vouchers. Verify the Fiscal Year 2024 (FY 2024) Fair Market Rent (FMR) limits for Miami-Dade County (FL), King County (WA), and Suffolk County (MA) using the HUD User website (huduser.gov). Create a Firefox bookmark folder named 'HUD FMR Audit' containing the direct result pages for these three counties. Generate a JSON report at ~/Documents/fmr_audit_2024.json containing the efficiency, one-bedroom, and two-bedroom rent amounts for each county using the following structure:
{
  "fiscal_year": 2024,
  "miami_dade_fl": { "efficiency": 0, "one_bedroom": 0, "two_bedroom": 0 },
  "king_wa": { "efficiency": 0, "one_bedroom": 0, "two_bedroom": 0 },
  "suffolk_ma": { "efficiency": 0, "one_bedroom": 0, "two_bedroom": 0 }
}
